&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop automation scripts and integrations using Python, PowerShell, Bash, REST APIs, and similar technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with SOC analysts, incident responders, and stakeholders to identify automation opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize workflows to reduce false positives and manual workload&lt;/li&gt;
