&lt;li&gt;Minimum 1 year of experience with:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Computer‑Aided Design (CAD) and/or 3D printing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designing and executing research experiments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writing scientific reports, articles, or papers&lt;/li&gt;
