&lt;li&gt;Minimum 6 months of experience with:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Laboratory work involving Unmanned Underwater Vehicles (UUVs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Field testing of UUV systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
